{"tid":2431692,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋]一套舊外國恐怖電影","createTime":"2021-03-03T23:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T10:10:57.000Z","uid":259335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4d46822c9852fec51a3ead70694a0027e85989f6","tid":2431692,"uid":259335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T23:33:53.000Z","msg":"1. 套野肯定係2000之前出嘅 <br />\n   (好舊 我估係1980s至1990s期間出)<br />\n2. 外國片 講英文嘅 <br />\n3. 印象中啲口音唔似英式 所以我估可能係美國片<br />\n4. 恐怖片<br />\n<br />\n劇情<br />\n1. 一班人 晚夜 去到一間工廠之類嘅地方<br />\n2. 啲怪物/惡魔(應該係被召喚出來)出現係間工廠到<br />\n3. 班人發現啲怪物 好似喪屍咁 傻傻下咁周圍行<br />\n4. 跟住班人整污糟自己 扮成怪物嘅一分仔咁行 得左<br />\n5. 結局係 兩個男人/一男一女(總之得幾條友) <br />\n    諗住搭lift走 點知架lift係直落地獄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b7525d4ac41319e7e5dbfb972e5a29035ade16","tid":2431692,"uid":50892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T23:40:09.000Z","msg":"The cabinet in the woods? 唔知係咪架你自己搵下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a546d4cbb70dd2deb49b25232d130e30f4cd0da","tid":2431692,"uid":259335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T23:55:12.000Z","msg":"套戲大部份時份都係間廠到拍 (好似係 80%肯定)<br />\n所以好少巿區/街道嘅鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n我自已都search左少少 已知唔係<br />\n全部為美國片<br />\nThe cabinet in the woods (2011)<br />\nDevil (2010)<br />\nThe Devil's Advocate (1997)<br />\nWishmaster (1997)<br />\nDemon Knight (1995)<br />\nNightbreed (1990)"},{"pid":"bb84c3d7a287da1520e83fab04c63d1e54039743","tid":2431692,"uid":34609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T00:05:17.000Z","msg":"係咪&quot;魔鬼屍餐&quot; 系列  ?"},{"pid":"d7234d0f4881422e445067424ec00326e190046a","tid":2431692,"uid":259335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb84c3d7a287da1520e83fab04c63d1e54039743","tid":2431692,"uid":34609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T00:05:17.000Z","msg":"係咪&quot;魔鬼屍餐&quot; 系列  ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T00:11:25.000Z","msg":"Jeepers Creepers系列 <br />\n睇一睇左 發現都唔係<br />\nThanks anyway"},{"pid":"c90100075b9fb7b6e685854b496da735d5aec54f","tid":2431692,"uid":259335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T00:16:56.000Z","msg":"我係google到 search左 <br />\nAmerican horror movie 1980s<br />\nAmerican horror movie 1990s<br />\n發現都好似唔見有咁 <br />\n<br />\n諗諗下都未必係美國片 <br />\n但應該係英文片<br />\n<br />\n同埋套野 我細個係 有線啲電影台睇到 (大概2000 ~ 2007)"},{"pid":"f3c75f61233407f5804020e281071fbfe6fa2346","tid":2431692,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T00:56:55.000Z","msg":"Silent hill"},{"pid":"94704ba8b305547559061d5d8a12e37d3397fa13","tid":2431692,"uid":259335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3c75f61233407f5804020e281071fbfe6fa2346","tid":2431692,"uid":116705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T00:56:55.000Z","msg":"Silent hill"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:03:50.000Z","msg":"非也 非也"},{"pid":"5ef61cb57d0333ca8f961357827966153f0ca7da","tid":2431692,"uid":355211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:08:19.000Z","msg":"Night of the Demons ?"},{"pid":"a93be0f4b94ea96c2f65df2a7640b4ab9f5631cd","tid":2431692,"uid":259335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ef61cb57d0333ca8f961357827966153f0ca7da","tid":2431692,"uid":355211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:08:19.000Z","msg":"Night of the Demons ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:09:11.000Z","msg":"呢套個feel似 但都係唔係"},{"pid":"9f05598ff22ab50547394f53cf0506de94bc8f82","tid":2431692,"uid":50506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:16:21.000Z","msg":"想搵返一套西片 係一班後生仔好似露營果時 圍住火堆講鬼故<br />\n記得其中一個鬼故係 一對夫婦揸露營車去旅行 個老公最後俾隻怪物殺左 吊左係車上面<br />\n過程中有幕係 兩公婆係車入面扑野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一個故仔係 個男主角去左一間凶屋<br />\n個女鬼不停重覆生前俾老豆殺既情形<br />\n男主角鍾意左個女鬼 所以想逃出命運 帶走個女鬼出屋<br />\n最後成功逃出左個命運<br />\n不過係樹下面解開個女鬼條頸圈之後<br />\n個女仔條頸就甩左...<br />\n<br />\n成班後生仔講完啲鬼故之後<br />\n其中一個後生仔突然發現原來佢地成班fd係去露營途中揸車 炒車出事<br />\n其他fd原來一早死左"},{"pid":"fb3a0cc3d588535324f2da69af13eb26014869ad","tid":2431692,"uid":44882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a546d4cbb70dd2deb49b25232d130e30f4cd0da","tid":2431692,"uid":259335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T23:55:12.000Z","msg":"套戲大部份時份都係間廠到拍 (好似係 80%肯定)<br />\n所以好少巿區/街道嘅鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n我自已都search左少少 已知唔係<br />\n全部為美國片<br />\nThe cabinet in the woods (2011)<br />\nDevil (2010)<br />\nThe Devil's Advocate (1997)<br />\nWishmaster (1997)<br />\nDemon Knight (1995)<br />\nNightbreed (1990)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:21:24.000Z","msg":"cabin in the woods致敬片黎<br />\n我睇你啲形容初初都以為係呢套<br />\n樓主可以試下係致敬list果度逐個逐個睇下係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得會有"},{"pid":"2ea1ae85bf9b63dffbaca1201dfdf3f3819bed31","tid":2431692,"uid":259335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3a0cc3d588535324f2da69af13eb26014869ad","tid":2431692,"uid":44882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a546d4cbb70dd2deb49b25232d130e30f4cd0da","tid":2431692,"uid":259335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T23:55:12.000Z","msg":"套戲大部份時份都係間廠到拍 (好似係 80%肯定)<br />\n所以好少巿區/街道嘅鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n我自已都search左少少 已知唔係<br />\n全部為美國片<br />\nThe cabinet in the woods (2011)<br />\nDevil (2010)<br />\nThe Devil's Advocate (1997)<br />\nWishmaster (1997)<br />\nDemon Knight (1995)<br />\nNightbreed (1990)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:21:24.000Z","msg":"cabin in the woods致敬片黎<br />\n我睇你啲形容初初都以為係呢套<br />\n樓主可以試下係致敬list果度逐個逐個睇下係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得會有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"好 ! 我試下先 Thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4406a